items.sentence: Let's not let our differences get in the way.
Tom dipped his French fries into the ketchup.
Tom looked at the moon through his telescope.
Tom did a lot of stupid things as a teenager.
Tom told me he thought that Mary was selfish.
Tom told me he thought that Mary was serious.
Tom told me he thought that Mary was outside.
Tom told me he thought that Mary was pleased.
Tom told me that he thought that Mary was OK.
Tom said that he heard Mary and John arguing.
